ary domain. On the next page, enter your details such as email address, and password to complete the process. Check “I agree to the terms and conditions” and hit next. ","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1,"offset":4554},"end":{"line":69,"column":323,"offset":4950}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Upon reaching confirmation page, you get confirmation of your subdomain and a request to click finish. ","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1,"offset":4952},"end":{"line":71,"column":104,"offset":5055}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1,"offset":4952},"end":{"line":71,"column":104,"offset":5055}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Step 3: Linking your website with GitHub Account","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":5,"offset":5061},"end":{"line":73,"column":53,"offset":5109}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1,"offset":5057},"end":{"line":73,"column":53,"offset":5109}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"raw","value":"<img src=\"/img/uploads/linking-your-website-with-github-account-.png    \">\n<br>\nOn the next page, you will get a link “Go back to dashboard”. Click it and you will be redirected to your website's dashboard with plenty of options to manage your site and account. ","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1,"offset":5111},"end":{"line":77,"column":183,"offset":5373}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In order to manage your website, you need a verified GitHub account and connect it with WebriQ account. ","position":{"start":{"line":79,"column":1,"offset":5375},"end":{"line":79,"column":105,"offset":5479}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":79,"column":1,"offset":5375},"end":{"line":79,"column":105,"offset":5479}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{